{"tha-ap255:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap255:0.2":"Thomakavagga ","tha-ap255:0.3":"Citakapujakattheraapadana ","tha-ap255:1.1":"“Anando nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap255:1.2":"sayambhu aparajito; ","tha-ap255:1.3":"Aranne parinibbayi, ","tha-ap255:1.4":"amanussamhi kanane. ","tha-ap255:2.1":"Devaloka idhagantva, ","tha-ap255:2.2":"citam katvanaham tada; ","tha-ap255:2.3":"Sariram tattha jhapesim, ","tha-ap255:2.4":"sakkaranca akasaham. ","tha-ap255:3.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap255:3.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap255:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap255:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap255:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap255:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap255:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap255:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma citakapujako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap255:6.1":"Citakapujakattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}